---
title: Catacombs Skip
hidden: false
---
Catacombs skips allow you to skip the major part of the catacombs without using glitches ou by using different kinds of [fall damages cancels](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel).

## How to perform this skip ?

### Glitchless Versions

- The first method **uses** [slope rolls](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#slope-rolls) and **requires** a specific equip load, as **shown** in [this video](https://youtu.be/BVtYZBgG0Wo) by m3dic on YouTube. It is very difficult and **requires** a lot of practice, also, RNG is involved for this method.
- The second method is way easier than the one above and only require specific pathing : [https://youtu.be/38Oipc17ErY](https://youtu.be/38Oipc17ErY) by m3dic on YouTube

### Glitched Versions

- The first method **uses** [delayed roll](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#delayed-rolls) , it is very easy and consistent :   [https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0](https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0) by aeiou on YouTube
- The second method **uses** [memerolls](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel#air-rolls), it is easy and consistent but require specific equip load : [https://youtu.be/LhZO6uND8wI?t=1648](https://youtu.be/LhZO6uND8wI?t=1648) by minitius on YouTube
